
Smart contract for BDNS and interchain functionalities


querySubdomain:  takes as input a subdomain name and outputs the list of validators and their associated endpoints for brick storages, anchoring services, message queues and the last hash of the subdomain state.
updateState: Update the state (eg. a  hash) of a  subdomain ledger.
registerSubdomain: Register a new subdomain. Depending on the governance smart contract, it could require approval (by vote) from others.



